{
  "stem": "23350.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from Russia, maybe we could somehow get to Palestine or whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But as soon as we hear there was the clear given that we can go back to our town, my father wouldn't hear of it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, oh, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because from generations they lived in this town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we arrived, and the first thing when we passed the bridge and we saw what this very big building, which was for hay, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was a wooden, big, enormous-- like a shed, but enormous one, built from wood for hay and straw.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father said, ah, everything's intact.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We came home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Our house was intact.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in actual fact, it would have been better if everything would have been burned down.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then we probably-- they would have probably survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They would have probably never stayed there, you see?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So when did you--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we had arrived, everything was intact.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Except in the center of the town, a lot of houses were burned down, because when the Germans arrived, the first thing what they did, they threw some bombs down everywhere.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what had hit actually was the center, half of the area from the houses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And our synagogue was burned down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was my sister and the two children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father, and me, and the two other sisters, not married ones.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My oldest brother was taken.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was in Pabianice, anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He lived in Pabianice, but they've taken him to very hard working-- they've taken him to a labor camp where he had to work on the railways.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was the hardest work you could have, with no food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As soon as the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Soon after they taking him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my other brother, they shot him.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
